CatDescriptText: All-Pro Chicken was part of All-Pro Enterprises, founded and owned by Brady Keys, Jr. (former running back for the Pittsburgh Steelers).  This particular franchise was owned by Willie Stargell, and it is remembered for offering free chicken when he hit a home run.
TitMainTitle: Exterior of Brady Keys' All-Pro Chicken restaurant with Plaza Beauty Salon and Eletrolux store in background
